## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the potential bias of sources. Some sources may present arguments that reflect specific organizational or political agendas. Additionally, the complexity of legal and ethical considerations surrounding the death penalty means that this report cannot cover all aspects of the debate comprehensively. Further research and analysis are recommended for a more in-depth understanding.